2022-01-19 21:49:37	<--	heat (~heat@sortix/contributor/heat) has quit (Read error: Connection reset by peer)
2022-01-19 21:49:41	topcat001	Chrome needs the `--use-gl=desktop --enable-features=VaapiVideoDecoder' flags (for X11).
2022-01-19 21:49:58	topcat001	the difference is dramatic
2022-01-19 21:50:59	topcat001	https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Hardware_video_acceleration
